Lockwood West https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lockwood_West 0 Harry Lockwood West (28 July 1905 – 28 March 1989) was a British actor. He was the father of actor Timothy West and the grandfather of actor Samuel West. Harry_Lockwood_West ( 28_July_1905 – 28_March_1989 ) was a_British_actor .
